*Story**
One upon a time there was a hare and a Tortois .They decide to have a rase.
The environmtnt was set up fore the rase by other animals in the forest .The rase began and hare started running 
very fast and was a head of Tortois who was very slow. 
After some time hare became very tired and took a nap under a tree thinking that Tortois is very slow .
But the Tortois slowly and steadily went a head of hare and won the rase . 
